'''Eyeblasters''' were a type of [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] ordered when undercover in her 'tough girl persona', and she took the drink atomized, not fizzed. Her [[Marriage/Legends|husband]] [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] did not enjoy them.<ref name="TG">''[[Tatooine Ghost]]''</ref>

